content.description:
Ed Rocks is the tallest and largest wall at TWS reaching upwards of 42 feet. It is located on the far right side of the TWS outcrop. The wall starts where the left end of Ed Rocks meets the Roof Arete Wall. This is a beautiful sunny location on an open hill.
